{"tid":1789432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再話風波平息左","createTime":"2019-12-19T10:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T13:24:51.000Z","uid":343063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9c82a96d6ee4a0167f9601a7432c3ce6984eac7b","tid":1789432,"uid":343063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:41:07.000Z","msg":"咪撚再休息啦<br />\n區選同人權法過左 我地都未贏架 <br />\n繼poly一戰後 非法集結改控暴動 手足判入獄冇手令都hack iphone拎證據 星火都被吿洗黑錢 7000萬凍結哂 仲有好多事 肯做嘢未？<br />\n光復香港時代革命唔係口號<br />\n香港人報仇唔係口號<br />\n係要實踐架 咪撚再休息啦 好嗎？<br />\n記唔記得五大訴求缺一不可呀？知唔知點解呀？<br />\n我地一日未爭取到 我地一日都未贏<br />\n和理非又好 勇武又好 和勇不分<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: green;\">光復香港 時代革命 <br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港人報仇<br />\n</span></em></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566b351ab8207375c46fa0fc1e8a93a07e6f8a92","tid":1789432,"uid":343063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:43:26.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b8b02ab375e8af5758c77235efac57f9c8cdf31b","tid":1789432,"uid":343063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:43:42.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b60227d6b3213ea274c184bd9b6bffcd7295abaa","tid":1789432,"uid":343063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:43:54.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"15100d3d4e955c3998c0514d4184b6608e9457c4","tid":1789432,"uid":343063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:44:07.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"7223cd27e18cdf29416ca1973d7bd147999212ed","tid":1789432,"uid":343063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:44:17.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"f4